        "highlight_text_color": "#caa876",
        "heading_size": 100,
        "content": "<h4><strong>Fused Core™ | The Foundation</strong></h4><p><em><strong>Waterproof, Orthopedic Utility</strong></em><em><br/></em>A rugged tarpaulin mattress that resists the elements and supports joints.</p><h4><strong>Beast | Fused Core™ + Better Than Ballistic™ Beast Cover</strong></h4><p><em><strong>Comfort and Dig-Proof Durability</strong></em><em><br/></em>Keep the waterproof, indestructible core. Add quilted padding and washable, eco-tough armor that resists claws, odors, and bacteria.</p><h4><strong>Nomad | Fused Core™ + Better Than Ballistic™ Beast Cover + Supportive Bolsters</strong></h4><p><em><strong>Tough Plush Luxury</strong></em><em><br/></em>Stay waterproof, washable, dig-proof, and odor-free. Add bolstered sides that turn the bed into a true home base for lounging.</p>",
