        },
        "text_WK8Dqm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Most “tough” pet brands focus on function alone — toughness for toughness’s sake. But dogs aren’t problems to be solved. They’re trail mates, co-pilots, backyard guardians, and kitchen-floor loafers. Our gear is built for real dogs, real messes, and real memories. We’re lifelong dog lovers, product designers, and adventurers who know firsthand: life with a dog is a glorious mess — from post-hike mud to rainy day naps. That’s why our durability goes beyond problem chewers. It’s designed for comfort. It’s a promise for every dog.</p>",
            "size": 100
          }
        },
