    "388f3454-ced6-4059-9e18-75ca70067528": {
      "type": "section-accordions",
      "blocks": {
        "text_RJVjU4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes Black Lab beds different?",
            "text": "<p>Every Signature Black Lab bed is built around our proprietary Fused Core™ waterproof mattress. Unlike traditional dog beds that allow moisture to reach the foam, Fused Core™ helps protect the support layer at the heart of the bed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_YajKN6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why are add-ons available?",
            "text": "<p>Because dogs grow and homes change. The modular design allows you to adapt the bed to your dog’s needs, your space, and your lifestyle without replacing the entire bed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_xenMjg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is Fused Core™?",
            "text": "<p>Fused Core™ is our fully sealed waterproof orthopedic mattress. Heat-welded seams help keep moisture out while solid orthopedic foam provides lasting support. It's the foundation inside every Signature Black Lab bed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_TNpKFC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are Black Lab beds waterproof?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. Every Signature bed is built around our Fused Core™ mattress is waterproof at its core. The removable outer covers are water-resistant and designed for everyday life, while the mattress itself helps protect against accidents, spills, and wet dogs.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_qCAWyn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I clean my bed?",
            "text": "<p>The removable outer covers can be machine washed. The Fused Core™ mattress can be wiped clean, hosed off, or sanitized as needed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_bf4pp3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is StayFresh™?",
            "text": "<p>StayFresh™ is our odor-fighting technology built into the outer covers. It helps combat odor-causing bacteria and continues working wash after wash.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_mJhcXp": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I buy extra covers?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. Extra covers are available so you can rotate styles, keep a spare for laundry day, or refresh the look of your bed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_gKErbA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Will the bed help with odors?",
            "text": "<p>A cleaner cover and a protected mattress work together to help reduce the buildup of odors over time. Because moisture stays out of the mattress, odors have fewer places to hide.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--18963859341627__388f3454-ced6-4059-9e18-75ca70067528-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the Fused Core™ crate-friendly?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, all our Fused Core™ mattresses are designed to fit into most standard size metal folding crates. Our 36” beds fit 36” crates, our 42” beds fit 42” crates, and our 48” beds fit 48” crates.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--18963859341627__388f3454-ced6-4059-9e18-75ca70067528-text-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "What size bed should I get?",
            "text": "<p>The appropriate bed size for your dog is determined by their length, not their weight. Measure your dog from the nose tip to the tail base to find the minimum bed length needed for them to stretch comfortably. Utilize the size guide tab on the product page for additional sizing information.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_i7gmx6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What type of foam do you use?",
            "text": "<p>We use solid orthopedic foam designed to provide consistent support and comfort. Unlike air-filled beds or loose-fill alternatives, orthopedic foam maintains its shape and support over time.</p>"
          }
        },
        "df788f7e-9fbe-404a-b7e1-b614c57066ae": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the Fused Core™ an orthopedic bed?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. The Fused Core™ provides comprehensive, uniform support, alleviating pressure on joints and aiding in pain relief for pets experiencing discomfort. Essential for older dogs with arthritis or hip and spine issues, it's can equally beneficial for younger dogs, offering crucial support to prevent potential future ailments.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--18963859341627__388f3454-ced6-4059-9e18-75ca70067528-text-3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which bed is right for my dog?",
            "text": "<h3>Utility</h3><p>Our waterproof foundation. Ideal for crates, travel, outdoor use, and everyday durability.</p><h3>Signature</h3><p>Our most popular bed. Combines Fused Core™, a quilted comfort layer, and a removable StayFresh™ cover.</p><h3>Signature Pillow</h3><p>Everything included in Signature, with added head support.</p><h3>Signature Bolster</h3><p>Surrounding bolsters create a cozy place for dogs who like to curl up or lean while resting.</p>"
          }
        },
        "303c4a03-a259-4a5e-b517-3efdadc7c8c9": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "title": "What does \"BETTER THAN BALLISTIC™\" mean?",
            "text": "<p>Other companies use materials labeled \"ballistic\" or \"rip-stop,\" which are often deemed proprietary. However, these materials tend to fall short on their claims. Oftentimes, these fabrics are non-recyclable, non-eco-friendly, and have been shown to degrade after the first wash.</p><p>Our fabrics are Better than Ballistic™ because:</p><ul><li>Made from Tougher than Nails Recycled Repreve™ Fabric</li><li>Eliminates odors</li><li>Eliminates 99.9% of bacteria</li><li>Triple layered for waterproof durability</li><li>Eco-friendly manufacturing process</li><li>Wash Less, saves money & time</li><li>Comfort, Style and sustainability for your pup</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "text_37xjLA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are the covers removable?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. Signature, Signature Pillow, and Signature Bolster beds feature removable covers designed for easy cleaning.</p>"
          }
        },
        "0f9535c7-1b4d-40a2-8042-374047f741fe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long should a Black Lab bed last?",
            "text": "<p>Black Lab beds are designed for years of daily use. By protecting the foam from moisture and contamination, Fused Core™ helps preserve the part of the bed that matters most.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--18963859341627__388f3454-ced6-4059-9e18-75ca70067528-text-4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are Black Lab beds made for large dogs?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. Our beds are available in sizes suitable for everything from small breeds to giant breeds, including Great Danes and Mastiffs.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_9M9T6H": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What if my dog is hard on beds?",
            "text": "<p>Black Lab beds are designed for durability and everyday life. While no fabric bed is indestructible, our materials and construction are chosen to withstand years of use by active dogs. and repeated washing.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
